{"tid":363354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國exchange開咩銀行戶口好？","createTime":"2017-08-17T14:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T15:35:06.000Z","uid":120774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"578edbecb7a19085350d1f811e72e174e9a13016","tid":363354,"uid":120774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲去過英國exchange?<br />\n想問下有邊間銀行好？<br />\n我見好多Student Account最少都要留係英國兩年或以上同埋有charge<br />\n<br />\n老母有HSBC Premier, 其實可以直接免費開個英國聯名戶口，又唔洗TT Charge。奈何老母唔識英文，activate唔到個戶口，結果冇開到。<br />\n<br />\n巴絲有咩高見"},{"pid":"657de3384bbdac87539a6ea010b52b98922cc356","tid":363354,"uid":50911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T15:21:31.000Z","msg":"用公事包裝一箱銀紙過去"},{"pid":"b30879506880efa91c1c7cf3a75989be47842e8f","tid":363354,"uid":103229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"HSBC 最方便 但其實好多銀行既卡都可以直接係個邊㩒(前題有銀聯) 但一定HSBC最方便架啦 實冇事 但好多都要收charge<br />\nExchange唔洗搞咁多嘢啦 你係個邊開咗戶口 又唔係長讀 冇乜所謂 因為開戶口仲要學校出封信比你架 個邊比較方便係如果有debit card 基本上唔洗帶銀包出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者Applepay 好多都accept<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9b68b2133ed8a07a729615b49b94bee22a1b65","tid":363354,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HSBC 最方便 但其實好多銀行既卡都可以直接係個邊㩒(前題有銀聯) 但一定HSBC最方便架啦 實冇事 但好多都要收charge<br />\nExchange唔洗搞咁多嘢啦 你係個邊開咗戶口 又唔係長讀 冇乜所謂 因為開戶口仲要學校出封信比你架 個邊比較方便係如果有debit card 基本上唔洗帶銀包出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者Applepay 好多都accept<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己就用緊lloyds bank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識好多人讀咗幾年都冇開戶口 有咩就直接碌卡/㩒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ac0fdf6d05cde5382fea7c8420cf58ac328d3b","tid":363354,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited